oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 1975 Annual Richland Fire Co. Carnival (16581)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Smathers, Ben, -1990; Wells, Kitty; Tubb, Ernest, 1914-1984; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and black on white) announcing the 1975 Annual Richland Fire Co. Carnival featuring performances by Ben Smathers, Kitty Wells, Ernest Tubb and others. Poster features metal photoplates of Ben Smathers and the Stoney Mountain Cloggers, Kitty Wells, Johnny Wright, and Ernest Tubb.
